I".<h2 id="solution">Solution:</h2>

<p>We apply the shifting technique to eliminate the history of the recurrence relation.</p>

\[\begin{align*}
        T(n + 1) - T(n) = \left[ (n + 1) + \sum_{i = 1}^{n}T(i) \right] - \left[ n + \sum_{i = 1}^{n - 1}T(i) \right] = 1 + T(n)
    \end{align*}\]

\[\qed\]
